<p>I need to get the id of the object clicked so I can use it in a query in the view.</p>  <p><em>template</em></p>  <pre><code>&lt;form action="/services/delpoll/" method="post"&gt;{% csrf_token %}        &lt;td&gt;&lt;input type="submit" id="{{b.id}}" class="delete_poll" value="Borrar"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;      &lt;/form&gt; </code></pre>  <p><em>view</em></p>  <pre><code>def delpoll(request):      connect_mysql = mdb.connect('*', '*', '*', '*')     cursorMYSQL = connect_mysql.cursor(mdb.cursors.DictCursor)      if request.method == 'POST':          id_poll = request.POST.get['delete_poll'];         cursorMYSQL.execute(""" delete from snmptt_listpolls where id='%s' """%(id_poll))          connect_mysql.commit()         connect_mysql.close()          return render_to_response("delpoll.html",{"message": 'post'} )       else:          return render_to_response("delpoll.html",{"message": 'no-post'} )   </code></pre>